commit.message: Added missing delimiter in long format (#265)
Enable writing cache only when suitable
Show uid/gid/permissions only if really available
Support for reading uid/gid/permissions from cache file (#265)
Don't move attic all the way up to invisible root
Prevent crash if entire tree is ignored in unpkg view (Fixes #262)
Use more reliable way to get absolute path (Fixes #261)
Refer to Jesus Herrera's build instructions for building on macOS
Wording and removed macOS arch maintainer section
Clear _newRoot when the DirTree is cleared (Fixes #259)
Ensure pkg label is enabled when needed
Ensure pkg block is visible when needed in pkg view (Fixes #258)
Show multi-selected PkgInfos as directories, not files (#258)
